{
  "text": "Proof of Proposition 2.13: This section of the proof also follows exactly the ideas set out in [CITATION_1] and [35, Chapter 6] but we include some of the details since there are a couple of added technicalities here: We will use the Coulomb gauge in order to re-write our equation, so set \u01eb small enough so that we can apply Theorem D.1. We have",
